パッケージ manhattan.template

  • クラスのサマリー 
    クラス 説明
    Earth
    Earth utility.
    EventFolder
    Utility for an event folder
    HorizontalPosition
    Position Latitude Longitude This class is immutable.
    Latitude
    Latitude [-90, 90] The value is rounded off to the fourth decimal position.
    Location
    Location Latitude (-180, 180) Longitude（-90, 90）Radius [0,∞) This class is IMMUTABLE.
    Longitude
    Longitude (-180, 180] If you input 200, then the value is considered -160.
    NamedDiscontinuityStructure
    Within each layer Bullen law v(r) = ArB is used.
    Raypath
    Raypath between a source at Raypath.sourceLocation and a receiver at Raypath.stationPosition
    This class is IMMUTABLE
    Station
    Information of station consisting of
    Station name, HorizontalPosition, Station network
    This class is IMMUTABLE.
    Trace
    Utility for a function y=f(x) This class is IMMUTABLE
    Utilities
    Utilities for a workpath containing event folders which have SAC files. also this contains various useful static methods.
